simple_means.memory_skill: aesthet 感觉 + ics …学，等于esthetics → 美学

tr: (art) the branch of philosophy dealing with beauty and taste (emphasizing the evaluative criteria that are applied to art)
example: traditional aesthetics assumed the existence of universal and timeless criteria of artistic value

value.boxr_value: in AM, also use 美国英语亦用 esthetics

value.def: Aesthetics is a branch of philosophy concerned with the study of the idea of beauty.

partsOfSpeech.dec: aesthet 感觉 + e → 对美有感觉的人 → 审美家
aesthet 感觉 + ic …的 → 对美有感觉的 → 审美的
aesthet 感觉 + ics …学，等于esthetics → 美学
an 无 + aesthet 感觉 + ic 某种药 → 使无感觉的药 → 麻醉剂
an 无 + esthes〔= esthet 感觉〕+ ia 某种病 → 无感觉 → 麻醉
